title: UML用例图-BL-20260626-02
tags: [UML 基线]
aliases: ["用例图-BL-20260626-02"]
---

@startuml
left to right direction
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
actor "招商业务员" as Sales
actor "运维工程师" as Ops
actor "库房人员" as WH
actor "财务人员" as Fin
actor "审批链" as Approver

rectangle "设备管理" {
  usecase "UC1: 监控设备校准有效期" as UC1
  usecase "UC2: 执行设备出库管控" as UC2
  usecase "UC3: 发起紧急出库审批" as UC3
  usecase "UC4: 执行设备归还检测" as UC4
  usecase "UC5: 录入初检结果" as UC5
  usecase "UC6: 执行全面复核" as UC6
  usecase "UC7: 处理检测偏差" as UC7
  usecase "UC8: 创建维修工单" as UC8
  usecase "UC9: 查看财务影响分析" as UC9
}

note right of UC1 : 合并BR-EQP-001/005\n覆盖库房内和已出租设备
note right of UC2 : 合并BR-EQP-002/003\n7天禁止出库+3天锁库
note right of UC3 : 基于BR-EQP-003\n三级审批流程
note right of UC4 : 合并BR-EQP-004/006/007/008/009/015/016\n统一归还检测入口
note right of UC7 : 合并BR-EQP-006/007/009/015/016\n分级预警+强制入库/创建工单
note right of UC8 : 基于BR-EQP-008\n自动创建P1级工单

Sales --> UC1
Sales --> UC2
Sales --> UC3
Ops --> UC4
Ops --> UC5
WH --> UC6
Ops --> UC7
Ops --> UC8
Fin --> UC9

UC2 .> UC1 : <<include>>
UC4 .> UC5 : <<include>>
UC4 .> UC6 : <<include>>
UC7 .> UC8 : <<extend>>
UC3 .> UC2 : <<extend>>
UC9 .> UC7 : <<extend>>

note on link #FFAAAA: 出库管控依赖校准监控
note on link #FFAAAA: 归还检测包含初检和复核
note on link #FFAAAA: 偏差过大时触发维修工单
note on link #FFAAAA: 锁库后可发起紧急审批
note on link #FFAAAA: 财务查看偏差处理影响

@enduml